---
title: Chinese-Style Cashew Chicken with Garlicky Rice and Veggies
description: All the flavours of a cheeky takeout treat, but served separately so that everyone in the family can enjoy what they love! Sriracha brings a little extra heat for the grown ups.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chinese-style-cashew-chicken-953f8eda.jpg
